prediction.sparql:
PREFIX dblp: <https://dblp.org/rdf/schema#>
SELECT ?name ( COUNT( ?pub ) AS ?count ) WHERE {
  ?pub dblp:authoredBy ?creator .
  ?creator dblp:creatorName ?name .
  ?pub dblp:publishedInStream <https://dblp.org/streams/journals/sigir> .
  FILTER ( REGEX( ?name , "M\\..*D\\." , "i" ) )
}
GROUP BY ?name
ORDER BY DESC ( ?count )

PREFIX datacite: <http://purl.org/spar/datacite/>
SELECT ?scheme ( COUNT( ?identifier ) AS ?count ) WHERE {
  ?publication datacite:hasIdentifier ?identifier .
  ?identifier datacite:usesIdentifierScheme ?scheme
}
GROUP BY ?scheme
ORDER BY DESC ( ?count )

PREFIX dblp: <https://dblp.org/rdf/schema#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
SELECT ?type ( COUNT( ?s ) AS ?count ) WHERE {
  ?s rdf:type ?type .
  FILTER ( ?type IN ( dblp:Article , dblp:Inproceedings , dblp:Book , dblp:Incollection ) )
}
GROUP BY ?type
ORDER BY DESC ( ?count )
